
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Page Not Found - 404</title>
    <link href="/assets/css/bootstrap/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body { background: #f8f9fa; }
        .error-container { margin-top: 10%; text-align: center; }
        .error-code { font-size: 6rem; font-weight: bold; color: #dc3545; }
        .error-message { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .btn-home { margin-top: 2rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container error-container">
        <div class="error-code">404</div>
        <div class="error-message">Oops! The page you are looking for does not exist.</div>
        <p>It might have been moved or deleted. Please check the URL or return to the homepage.</p>
        <a href="/index.aspx" class="btn btn-primary btn-home">Go to Homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
